rows.label: qev050907_MSG0001
rows.name: Hngh... I cannot say the result is unexpected.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0002
rows.name: Regret burns me to my core, and yet there is more.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0003
rows.name: It is almost as though I feel...relieved.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0004
rows.name: Perhaps it is proof that I am still soft inside.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_JNK0010
rows.name: Praise

rows.label: qev050907_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Gu Ladha that she is an excellent Skell pilot.

rows.label: qev050907_JNK0020
rows.name: Listen

rows.label: qev050907_SEL0021
rows.name: Say nothing.

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0005
rows.name: I...am?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0006
rows.name:
I do feel more at home in the cockpit than in ground
combat, that is true.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0007
rows.name:
Well, I am thrilled to hear that I at least kept you on
your toes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0008
rows.name:
And though it shames me to admit it, there is a part of
me that needed to hear as much from you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0009
rows.name:
Hmm... No. Putting it that way still focuses on the
negative.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0010
rows.name:
Your help has given me confidence and knowledge
both.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0011
rows.name: Thank you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0012
rows.name: Heh. You are kind to keep silent.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0013
rows.name:
In times past, I would have taken such consideration
for pity and thought it a great insult.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0014
rows.name: But coming from you, it feels almost...nice.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0015
rows.name: I apologize for taking so much of your time and effort.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0016
rows.name:
But I feel that meeting you has shown me a new path
forward.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0017
rows.name:
Where it leads remains unseen, and I would be lying to
say I walk it without fear.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0018
rows.name: But I have just enough courage to try.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0019
rows.name: It was you who sparked that within me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0020
rows.name: I am thankful for our meeting.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0021
rows.name:
It will take time, but I swear to you that I will become
a worthy Wrothian fighter.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0022
rows.name: I hope we can meet again when that day comes![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0023
rows.name: Until then, let us part on that promise.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050907_MSG0024
rows.name: ...Be well, friend.[ST:wait ]
